title: Ace Lightning
description:
Thirteen-year-old Mark Hollander has just moved to America from England.  When he plays a computer game during a lightning storm, the characters within it come to life, including superhero Ace Lightning and the gang of evil villains he fights.  Predictably, chaos results.

Episodes 1-26, 27, 29, and 31.  Episodes 1-26 are avi files; 27, 29, and 31 are smaller mp4s.
